  "detailed_description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/e92eb677d683f18017b6691cb760fd7e.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=616 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/e92eb677d683f18017b6691cb760fd7e.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Sandy's Great Escape is a charming, pixel art puzzle game with nostalgic box pushing mechanics and a forgiving rewind mechanic. Death is never the end for Sandy, as you magically respawn and use your shell to help navigate through different obstacles. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/faafb1ba9652ee90884a0e7bd4a27664.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/faafb1ba9652ee90884a0e7bd4a27664.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/faafb1ba9652ee90884a0e7bd4a27664.mp4?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each of the four themed worlds adds unique mechanics to the field, giving even the most crabby player hours of entertainment with 100 levels in their claws. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/8754ab7b5e560abc4c99f7adca79a4bc.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/8754ab7b5e560abc4c99f7adca79a4bc.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/8754ab7b5e560abc4c99f7adca79a4bc.mp4?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And if thats not enough...<br><br>Perfect levels and earn currency to spin at the \"Gachapon-d\" to win over 40 unique skins!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/2eeb2a2febbf52f70a09c63c434b5cb3.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/2eeb2a2febbf52f70a09c63c434b5cb3.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/2eeb2a2febbf52f70a09c63c434b5cb3.mp4?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Snap to the beat with the nostalgic chiptune soundtrack!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/ea0d5732999ea8b1088e1263fa90f564.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/ea0d5732999ea8b1088e1263fa90f564.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/ea0d5732999ea8b1088e1263fa90f564.mp4?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And did we mention CRAB FACTS?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/f2ce970182dcf507c862acc8a8a2a878.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/f2ce970182dcf507c862acc8a8a2a878.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/f2ce970182dcf507c862acc8a8a2a878.mp4?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game was originally created for the SD IGDA 2020 Game Jam, and won 1st place. Sandy's Great Escape was created in GameMaker.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/3c30e865f8d47bc8e01d16e3cdf9a34f.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=616 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/3c30e865f8d47bc8e01d16e3cdf9a34f.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/e92eb677d683f18017b6691cb760fd7e.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=616 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/e92eb677d683f18017b6691cb760fd7e.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Sandy's Great Escape is a charming, pixel art puzzle game with nostalgic box pushing mechanics and a forgiving rewind mechanic. Death is never the end for Sandy, as you magically respawn and use your shell to help navigate through different obstacles. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/faafb1ba9652ee90884a0e7bd4a27664.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/faafb1ba9652ee90884a0e7bd4a27664.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/faafb1ba9652ee90884a0e7bd4a27664.mp4?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each of the four themed worlds adds unique mechanics to the field, giving even the most crabby player hours of entertainment with 100 levels in their claws. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/8754ab7b5e560abc4c99f7adca79a4bc.poster.avif?t=1697731230\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/8754ab7b5e560abc4c99f7adca79a4bc.webm?t=1697731230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><